---
title: Oven-Baked Chorizo & Sweetcorn Risotto with Rocket & Balsamic Vinegar
description: If you thought the secret to a perfect creamy risotto was stirring for hours on end, think again. With only fifteen minutes of hands-on cooking time required, this recipe is the perfect thing to knock together midweek. Bursting with delicious flavours and served alongside a fresh rocket salad, this colourful dish is guaranteed to delight even the fussiest of eaters. No mealtime meltdowns in sight!
